&lt;p>Visit the &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io">Hugo&lt;/a> website!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Tutorial: Install Hugo by Asdf</title><link>https://blog.caiolul.com/blog/posts/install-hugo-by-asdf/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.caiolul.com/blog/posts/install-hugo-by-asdf/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>This is a guide to install Hugo by Asdf.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="install-asdf">Install Asdf&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>First, install Asdf by following the instructions on the &lt;a href="https://asdf-vm.com/#/core-manage-asdf-vm">official website&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="install-hugo">Install Hugo&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>After installing Asdf, run the following command to install Hugo:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>asdf plugin add hugo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># or&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>asdf plugin add hugo https://github.com/NeoHsu/asdf-hugo.git
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Then, install the desired version of Hugo:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Show all installable versions&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>asdf list-all hugo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Install specific version&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>asdf install hugo latest
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Set a version globally (on your ~/.tool-versions file)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>asdf global hugo latest
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Now hugo commands are available&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>hugo version
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Extended for builds for Sass/SCSS:&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>